SELECT
	[SysSchema].[Name] [Name],
	MAX([SysLocalizableValue].[ModifiedOn]) [MaxModifiedOn]
FROM
	[dbo].[SysLocalizableValue] WITH(NOLOCK)
	INNER JOIN [dbo].[SysSchema] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([SysSchema].[Id] = [SysLocalizableValue].[SysSchemaId])
WHERE
	[SysLocalizableValue].[SysPackageId] IN (
SELECT
	[SysPackage].[Id]
FROM
	[dbo].[SysPackage] WITH(NOLOCK)
WHERE
	[SysPackage].[SysWorkspaceId] = @P1)
	AND [SysSchema].[ManagerName] = @P2
GROUP BY
	[SysSchema].[Name]

SELECT
	[SysSchema].[Id] [Id],
	[SysSchema].[ModifiedOn] [ModifiedOn],
	[SysSchema].[Checksum] [Checksum],
	[SysSchema].[UId] [UId],
	[SysSchema].[Name] [Name],
	[SysSchema].[ExtendParent] [ExtendParent],
	[SysSchema].[DenyExtending] [DenyExtending],
	[SysSchemaParent].[UId] [ParentUId],
	[SysPackage].[UId] [PackageUId],
	[SysPackage].[Name] [PackageName],
	[SysPackage].[Position] [PackagePosition],
	[SysSchemaProperty].[Name] [PropertyName],
	[SysSchemaProperty].[Value] [PropertyValue],
	[SysSchema].[MetaDataModifiedOn] [MetaDataModifiedOn],
	[SysSchema].[Descriptor] [Descriptor]
FROM
	[dbo].[SysSchema] WITH(NOLOCK)
	INNER JOIN [dbo].[SysPackage] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([SysPackage].[Id] = [SysSchema].[SysPackageId])
	LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[SysSchemaProperty] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([SysSchemaProperty].[SysSchemaId] = [SysSchema].[Id])
	LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[SysSchema] [SysSchemaParent] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([SysSchemaParent].[Id] = [SysSchema].[ParentId])
WHERE
	[SysPackage].[SysWorkspaceId] = @P1
	AND [SysSchema].[ManagerName] = @P2
ORDER BY
	[SysSchema].[Name] ASC,
	[SysSchema].[UId] ASC,
	[SysPackage].[Name] ASC

messageObject.SQL:
SELECT
	[SysPackage].[Position] [PackagePosition],
	(
SELECT
	MAX([SysPackageHierarchy].[Level])
FROM
	[dbo].[SysPackageHierarchy] WITH(NOLOCK)
WHERE
	[SysPackageHierarchy].[BaseSysPackageId] = [ResourceSelect].[PackageId]) [PackageLevel],
	[ResourceSelect].[SchemaId] [SchemaId],
	[ResourceSelect].[SchemaUId] [SchemaUId],
	[ResourceSelect].[SchemaName] [SchemaName],
	[ResourceSelect].[PackageName] [PackageName],
	[ResourceSelect].[PackageId] [PackageId],
	[ResourceSelect].[CultureId] [CultureId],
	[ResourceSelect].[ModifiedOn] [ModifiedOn],
	[ResourceSelect].[Key] [Key],
	[ResourceSelect].[Value] [Value],
	[ResourceSelect].[ResourceType] [ResourceType],
	[ResourceSelect].[ImageData] [ImageData]
FROM
	(
SELECT
	[LocalizableValue].[SysSchemaId] [SchemaId],
	[SysSchema].[UId] [SchemaUId],
	[SysSchema].[Name] [SchemaName],
	[SysPackage].[Name] [PackageName],
	[LocalizableValue].[SysPackageId] [PackageId],
	[LocalizableValue].[SysCultureId] [CultureId],
	[LocalizableValue].[ModifiedOn] [ModifiedOn],
	[LocalizableValue].[Key] [Key],
	[LocalizableValue].[Value] [Value],
	[LocalizableValue].[ResourceType] [ResourceType],
	[LocalizableValue].[ImageData] [ImageData]
FROM
	[dbo].[SysLocalizableValue] [LocalizableValue] WITH(NOLOCK)
	INNER JOIN [dbo].[SysPackage] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([SysPackage].[Id] = [LocalizableValue].[SysPackageId])
	INNER JOIN [dbo].[SysSchema] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([SysSchema].[Id] = [LocalizableValue].[SysSchemaId])
WHERE
	[SysPackage].[SysWorkspaceId] = @P1
	AND [LocalizableValue].[SysSchemaId] IN (@P2, @P3)) [ResourceSelect]
	INNER JOIN [dbo].[SysPackage] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([SysPackage].[Id] = [ResourceSelect].[PackageId])
ORDER BY
	[PackageLevel] DESC,
	[PackagePosition] DESC,
	[PackageName] ASC

SELECT
	MAX([SysPackageHierarchy].[Level])

	[dbo].[SysPackageHierarchy] WITH(NOLOCK)
WHERE
	[SysPackageHierarchy].[BaseSysPackageId] = [ResourceSelect].[PackageId]) [PackageLevel],
	[ResourceSelect].[SchemaId] [SchemaId],
	[ResourceSelect].[SchemaUId] [SchemaUId],
	[ResourceSelect].[SchemaName] [SchemaName],
	[ResourceSelect].[PackageName] [PackageName],
	[ResourceSelect].[PackageId] [PackageId],
	[ResourceSelect].[CultureId] [CultureId],
	[ResourceSelect].[ModifiedOn] [ModifiedOn],
	[ResourceSelect].[Key] [Key],
	[ResourceSelect].[Value] [Value],
	[ResourceSelect].[ResourceType] [ResourceType],
	[ResourceSelect].[ImageData] [ImageData]
FROM
	(
SELECT
	[LocalizableValue].[SysSchemaId] [SchemaId],
	[SysSchema].[UId] [SchemaUId],
	[SysSchema].[Name] [SchemaName],
	[SysPackage].[Name] [PackageName],
	[LocalizableValue].[SysPackageId] [PackageId],
	[LocalizableValue].[SysCultureId] [CultureId],
	[LocalizableValue].[ModifiedOn] [ModifiedOn],
	[LocalizableValue].[Key] [Key],
	[LocalizableValue].[Value] [Value],
	[LocalizableValue].[ResourceType] [ResourceType],
	[LocalizableValue].[ImageData] [ImageData]
FROM
	[dbo].[SysLocalizableValue] [LocalizableValue] WITH(NOLOCK)
	INNER JOIN [dbo].[SysPackage] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([SysPackage].[Id] = [LocalizableValue].[SysPackageId])
	INNER JOIN [dbo].[SysSchema] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([SysSchema].[Id] = [LocalizableValue].[SysSchemaId])
WHERE
	[SysPackage].[SysWorkspaceId] = @P1
	AND [LocalizableValue].[SysSchemaId] IN (@P2, @P3)) [ResourceSelect]
	INNER JOIN [dbo].[SysPackage] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([SysPackage].[Id] = [ResourceSelect].[PackageId])
ORDER BY
	[PackageLevel] DESC,
	[PackagePosition] DESC,
	[PackageName] ASC

SELECT

FROM
	[dbo].[SysPackageHierarchy] WITH(NOLOCK)
WHERE
	[SysPackageHierarchy].[BaseSysPackageId] = [ResourceSelect].[PackageId]) [PackageLevel],
	[ResourceSelect].[SchemaId] [SchemaId],
	[ResourceSelect].[SchemaUId] [SchemaUId],
	[ResourceSelect].[SchemaName] [SchemaName],
	[ResourceSelect].[PackageName] [PackageName],
	[ResourceSelect].[PackageId] [PackageId],
	[ResourceSelect].[CultureId] [CultureId],
	[ResourceSelect].[ModifiedOn] [ModifiedOn],
	[ResourceSelect].[Key] [Key],
	[ResourceSelect].[Value] [Value],
	[ResourceSelect].[ResourceType] [ResourceType],
	[ResourceSelect].[ImageData] [ImageData]
FROM
	(
SELECT
	[LocalizableValue].[SysSchemaId] [SchemaId],
	[SysSchema].[UId] [SchemaUId],
	[SysSchema].[Name] [SchemaName],
	[SysPackage].[Name] [PackageName],
	[LocalizableValue].[SysPackageId] [PackageId],
	[LocalizableValue].[SysCultureId] [CultureId],
	[LocalizableValue].[ModifiedOn] [ModifiedOn],
	[LocalizableValue].[Key] [Key],
	[LocalizableValue].[Value] [Value],
	[LocalizableValue].[ResourceType] [ResourceType],
	[LocalizableValue].[ImageData] [ImageData]
FROM
	[dbo].[SysLocalizableValue] [LocalizableValue] WITH(NOLOCK)
	INNER JOIN [dbo].[SysPackage] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([SysPackage].[Id] = [LocalizableValue].[SysPackageId])
	INNER JOIN [dbo].[SysSchema] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([SysSchema].[Id] = [LocalizableValue].[SysSchemaId])
WHERE
	[SysPackage].[SysWorkspaceId] = @P1
	AND [LocalizableValue].[SysSchemaId] IN (@P2, @P3, @P4)) [ResourceSelect]
	INNER JOIN [dbo].[SysPackage] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([SysPackage].[Id] = [ResourceSelect].[PackageId])
ORDER BY
	[PackageLevel] DESC,
	[PackagePosition] DESC,
	[PackageName] ASC

	[LocalizableValue].[ModifiedOn] [ModifiedOn],

WHERE
	[SysPackageHierarchy].[BaseSysPackageId] = [ResourceSelect].[PackageId]) [PackageLevel],
	[ResourceSelect].[SchemaId] [SchemaId],
	[ResourceSelect].[SchemaUId] [SchemaUId],
	[ResourceSelect].[SchemaName] [SchemaName],
	[ResourceSelect].[PackageName] [PackageName],
	[ResourceSelect].[PackageId] [PackageId],
	[ResourceSelect].[CultureId] [CultureId],
	[ResourceSelect].[ModifiedOn] [ModifiedOn],
	[ResourceSelect].[Key] [Key],
	[ResourceSelect].[Value] [Value],
	[ResourceSelect].[ResourceType] [ResourceType],
	[ResourceSelect].[ImageData] [ImageData]
FROM
	(
SELECT
	[LocalizableValue].[SysSchemaId] [SchemaId],
	[SysSchema].[UId] [SchemaUId],
	[SysSchema].[Name] [SchemaName],
	[SysPackage].[Name] [PackageName],
	[LocalizableValue].[SysPackageId] [PackageId],
	[LocalizableValue].[SysCultureId] [CultureId],
	[LocalizableValue].[ModifiedOn] [ModifiedOn],
	[LocalizableValue].[Key] [Key],
	[LocalizableValue].[Value] [Value],
	[LocalizableValue].[ResourceType] [ResourceType],
	[LocalizableValue].[ImageData] [ImageData]
FROM
	[dbo].[SysLocalizableValue] [LocalizableValue] WITH(NOLOCK)
	INNER JOIN [dbo].[SysPackage] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([SysPackage].[Id] = [LocalizableValue].[SysPackageId])
	INNER JOIN [dbo].[SysSchema] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([SysSchema].[Id] = [LocalizableValue].[SysSchemaId])
WHERE
	[SysPackage].[SysWorkspaceId] = @P1
	AND [LocalizableValue].[SysSchemaId] IN (@P2, @P3)) [ResourceSelect]
	INNER JOIN [dbo].[SysPackage] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([SysPackage].[Id] = [ResourceSelect].[PackageId])
ORDER BY
	[PackageLevel] DESC,
	[PackagePosition] DESC,
	[PackageName] ASC

	[LocalizableValue].[ModifiedOn] [ModifiedOn],

	[ResourceSelect].[ModifiedOn] [ModifiedOn],

	[LocalizableValue].[SysPackageId] [PackageId],
	[LocalizableValue].[SysCultureId] [CultureId],
	[LocalizableValue].[ModifiedOn] [ModifiedOn],
	[LocalizableValue].[Key] [Key],
	[LocalizableValue].[Value] [Value],

	[dbo].[SysLocalizableValue] [LocalizableValue] WITH(NOLOCK)

SELECT

	[dbo].[SysPackageHierarchy] WITH(NOLOCK)
WHERE
	[SysPackageHierarchy].[BaseSysPackageId] = [ResourceSelect].[PackageId]) [PackageLevel],
	[ResourceSelect].[SchemaId] [SchemaId],
	[ResourceSelect].[SchemaUId] [SchemaUId],
	[ResourceSelect].[SchemaName] [SchemaName],
	[ResourceSelect].[PackageName] [PackageName],
	[ResourceSelect].[PackageId] [PackageId],
	[ResourceSelect].[CultureId] [CultureId],
	[ResourceSelect].[ModifiedOn] [ModifiedOn],
	[ResourceSelect].[Key] [Key],
	[ResourceSelect].[Value] [Value],
	[ResourceSelect].[ResourceType] [ResourceType],
	[ResourceSelect].[ImageData] [ImageData]
FROM
	(
SELECT
	[LocalizableValue].[SysSchemaId] [SchemaId],
	[SysSchema].[UId] [SchemaUId],
	[SysSchema].[Name] [SchemaName],
	[SysPackage].[Name] [PackageName],
	[LocalizableValue].[SysPackageId] [PackageId],
	[LocalizableValue].[SysCultureId] [CultureId],
	[LocalizableValue].[ModifiedOn] [ModifiedOn],
	[LocalizableValue].[Key] [Key],
	[LocalizableValue].[Value] [Value],
	[LocalizableValue].[ResourceType] [ResourceType],
	[LocalizableValue].[ImageData] [ImageData]
FROM
	[dbo].[SysLocalizableValue] [LocalizableValue] WITH(NOLOCK)
	INNER JOIN [dbo].[SysPackage] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([SysPackage].[Id] = [LocalizableValue].[SysPackageId])
	INNER JOIN [dbo].[SysSchema] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([SysSchema].[Id] = [LocalizableValue].[SysSchemaId])
WHERE
	[SysPackage].[SysWorkspaceId] = @P1
	AND [LocalizableValue].[SysSchemaId] IN (@P2, @P3, @P4)) [ResourceSelect]
	INNER JOIN [dbo].[SysPackage] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([SysPackage].[Id] = [ResourceSelect].[PackageId])
ORDER BY
	[PackageLevel] DESC,
	[PackagePosition] DESC,
	[PackageName] ASC

	[SysModule].[Code] [Module],
	(
SELECT
	[Name]
FROM
	[dbo].[VwSysClientUnitSchema] WITH(NOLOCK)
WHERE
	[SysWorkspaceId] = @SysWorkspaceId
	AND [UId] = [SysModule].[SectionModuleSchemaUId]) [SectionModule],
	(
SELECT
	[Name]
FROM
	[dbo].[VwSysClientUnitSchema] WITH(NOLOCK)
WHERE
	[SysWorkspaceId] = @SysWorkspaceId
	AND [UId] = [SysModule].[SectionSchemaUId]) [SectionSchema],
	(
SELECT
	[Name]
FROM
	[dbo].[VwSysClientUnitSchema] WITH(NOLOCK)
WHERE
	[SysWorkspaceId] = @SysWorkspaceId
	AND [UId] = [SysModule].[CardModuleUId]) [CardModule],
	(
SELECT
	[Name]
FROM
	[dbo].[VwSysClientUnitSchema] WITH(NOLOCK)
WHERE
	[SysWorkspaceId] = @SysWorkspaceId
	AND [UId] = [SysModule].[CardSchemaUId]) [CardSchema],
	[SysModule].[Attribute] [Attribute],
	[SysModule].[TypeColumnValue] [ModuleTypeColumnValue],
	(
SELECT
	[Name]
FROM
	[dbo].[VwSysClientUnitSchema] WITH(NOLOCK)
WHERE
	[SysWorkspaceId] = @SysWorkspaceId
	AND [UId] = [SysModuleEdit].[CardSchemaUId]) [CardSchemaPage],
	(
SELECT
	[Name]
FROM
	[dbo].[VwSysClientUnitSchema] WITH(NOLOCK)
WHERE
	[SysWorkspaceId] = @SysWorkspaceId
	AND [UId] = [SysModuleEdit].[MiniPageSchemaUId]) [MiniPageSchema],
	[SysModuleEdit].[Id] [ModuleEditId],
	[SysModuleEdit].[ActionKindName] [ActionName],
	[SysModuleEdit].[TypeColumnValue] [TypeColumnValue],
	[SysModuleEntity].[SysEntitySchemaUId] [SysEntitySchemaUId],
	[SysModuleInWorkplace].[SysWorkplaceId] [ShowInWorkplace],
	[SysModule].[Caption] [ModuleCaption],
	[SysModule].[ModuleHeader] [ModuleHeader],
	[SysModuleEdit].[ActionKindCaption] [ActionCaption],
	[SysModuleEdit].[PageCaption] [PageCaption],
	[SysModuleLcz].[Caption] [ModuleCaptionLcz],
	[SysModuleLcz].[ModuleHeader] [ModuleHeaderLcz],
	[SysModuleEditLcz].[ActionKindCaption] [ActionCaptionLcz],
	[SysModuleEditLcz].[PageCaption] [PageCaptionLcz]
FROM
	[dbo].[SysModule] WITH(NOLOCK)
	LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[SysModuleInWorkplace] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([SysModuleInWorkplace].[SysModuleId] = [SysModule].[Id]
	AND [SysModuleInWorkplace].[SysWorkplaceId] = @P1)
	LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[SysModuleEdit] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([SysModuleEdit].[SysModuleEntityId] = [SysModule].[SysModuleEntityId])
	LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[SysModuleEntity] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([SysModuleEntity].[Id] = [SysModuleEdit].[SysModuleEntityId])
	LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[SysModuleLcz] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([SysModuleLcz].[RecordId] = [SysModule].[Id]
	AND [SysModuleLcz].[SysCultureId] = @P2)
	LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[SysModuleEditLcz] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([SysModuleEditLcz].[RecordId] = [SysModuleEdit].[Id]
	AND [SysModuleEditLcz].[SysCultureId] = @P3)
WHERE
	NOT [SysModule].[SectionModuleSchemaUId] IS NULL
	AND NOT [SysModule].[SysModuleEntityId] IN (
SELECT
	[SysModuleEntityId]
FROM
	[dbo].[SysModuleEntityInPortal] WITH(NOLOCK))
ORDER BY
	[SysModuleInWorkplace].[Position] ASC,
	[SysModuleEdit].[Position] ASC

SELECT
	[SysPackage].[Position] [PackagePosition],
	(
SELECT
	MAX([SysPackageHierarchy].[Level])
FROM
	[dbo].[SysPackageHierarchy] WITH(NOLOCK)
WHERE
	[SysPackageHierarchy].[BaseSysPackageId] = [ResourceSelect].[PackageId]) [PackageLevel],
	[ResourceSelect].[SchemaId] [SchemaId],
	[ResourceSelect].[SchemaUId] [SchemaUId],
	[ResourceSelect].[SchemaName] [SchemaName],
	[ResourceSelect].[PackageName] [PackageName],
	[ResourceSelect].[PackageId] [PackageId],
	[ResourceSelect].[CultureId] [CultureId],
	[ResourceSelect].[ModifiedOn] [ModifiedOn],
	[ResourceSelect].[Key] [Key],
	[ResourceSelect].[Value] [Value],
	[ResourceSelect].[ResourceType] [ResourceType],
	[ResourceSelect].[ImageData] [ImageData]
FROM
	(
SELECT
	[LocalizableValue].[SysSchemaId] [SchemaId],
	[SysSchema].[UId] [SchemaUId],
	[SysSchema].[Name] [SchemaName],
	[SysPackage].[Name] [PackageName],
	[LocalizableValue].[SysPackageId] [PackageId],
	[LocalizableValue].[SysCultureId] [CultureId],
	[LocalizableValue].[ModifiedOn] [ModifiedOn],
	[LocalizableValue].[Key] [Key],
	[LocalizableValue].[Value] [Value],
	[LocalizableValue].[ResourceType] [ResourceType],
	[LocalizableValue].[ImageData] [ImageData]
FROM
	[dbo].[SysLocalizableValue] [LocalizableValue] WITH(NOLOCK)
	INNER JOIN [dbo].[SysPackage] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([SysPackage].[Id] = [LocalizableValue].[SysPackageId])
	INNER JOIN [dbo].[SysSchema] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([SysSchema].[Id] = [LocalizableValue].[SysSchemaId])
WHERE
	[SysPackage].[SysWorkspaceId] = @P1
	AND [LocalizableValue].[SysSchemaId] IN (@P2, @P3)) [ResourceSelect]
	INNER JOIN [dbo].[SysPackage] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([SysPackage].[Id] = [ResourceSelect].[PackageId])
ORDER BY
	[PackageLevel] DESC,
	[PackagePosition] DESC,
	[PackageName] ASC

SELECT
	[SysWorkplace].[Id],
	[SysWorkplace].[Position],
	[SysWorkplace].[Name],
	[SysWorkplace].[IsPersonal],
	[SysWorkplace].[LoaderId],
	(
SELECT
	[Name]
FROM
	[dbo].[VwSysClientUnitSchema] WITH(NOLOCK)
WHERE
	[SysWorkspaceId] = @SysWorkspaceId
	AND [UId] = [SysWorkplace].[LoaderId]) [LoaderName],
	[SysModuleInWorkplace].[SysModuleId],
	[SysModuleInWorkplace].[Position] [ModulePosition],
	[SysModule].[Caption] [SysModuleCaption],
	[SysModule].[Code] [SysModuleName],
	(
SELECT
	[Name]
FROM
	[dbo].[VwSysClientUnitSchema] WITH(NOLOCK)
WHERE
	[SysWorkspaceId] = @SysWorkspaceId
	AND [UId] = [SysModule].[SectionSchemaUId]) [SectionModule],
	(
SELECT
	[Name]
FROM
	[dbo].[VwSysClientUnitSchema] WITH(NOLOCK)
WHERE
	[SysWorkspaceId] = @SysWorkspaceId
	AND [UId] = [SysModule].[SectionModuleSchemaUId]) [SectionModuleSchema],
	[SysWorkplaceLcz].[Name] [NameLcz]
FROM
	[dbo].[SysWorkplace] WITH(NOLOCK)
	LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[SysModuleInWorkplace] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([SysModuleInWorkplace].[SysWorkplaceId] = [SysWorkplace].[Id])
	LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[SysModule] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([SysModule].[Id] = [SysModuleInWorkplace].[SysModuleId])
	LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[SysWorkplaceLcz] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([SysWorkplaceLcz].[RecordId] = [SysWorkplace].[Id]
	AND [SysWorkplaceLcz].[SysCultureId] = @P3)
WHERE
	EXISTS (
SELECT
	1
FROM
	[dbo].[SysAdminUnitInWorkplace] WITH(NOLOCK)
WHERE
	EXISTS (
SELECT
	1
FROM
	[dbo].[SysAdminUnitInRole] WITH(NOLOCK)
	INNER JOIN [dbo].[SysAdminUnit] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([SysAdminUnit].[Id] = [SysAdminUnitInRole].[SysAdminUnitRoleId])
WHERE
	[SysAdminUnitInRole].[SysAdminUnitId] = @P1
	AND [SysAdminUnitInWorkplace].[SysAdminUnitId] = [SysAdminUnit].[Id])
	AND [SysWorkplace].[Id] = [SysAdminUnitInWorkplace].[SysWorkplaceId])
	AND [SysWorkplace].[SysApplicationClientTypeId] = @P2
ORDER BY
	[SysWorkplace].[Position] ASC,
	[SysWorkplace].[Name] ASC,
	[SysModuleInWorkplace].[Position] ASC

SELECT
	[SysPackage].[Position] [PackagePosition],
	(
SELECT
	MAX([SysPackageHierarchy].[Level])
FROM
	[dbo].[SysPackageHierarchy] WITH(NOLOCK)
WHERE
	[SysPackageHierarchy].[BaseSysPackageId] = [ResourceSelect].[PackageId]) [PackageLevel],
	[ResourceSelect].[SchemaId] [SchemaId],
	[ResourceSelect].[SchemaUId] [SchemaUId],
	[ResourceSelect].[SchemaName] [SchemaName],
	[ResourceSelect].[PackageName] [PackageName],
	[ResourceSelect].[PackageId] [PackageId],
	[ResourceSelect].[CultureId] [CultureId],
	[ResourceSelect].[ModifiedOn] [ModifiedOn],
	[ResourceSelect].[Key] [Key],
	[ResourceSelect].[Value] [Value],
	[ResourceSelect].[ResourceType] [ResourceType],
	[ResourceSelect].[ImageData] [ImageData]
FROM
	(
SELECT
	[LocalizableValue].[SysSchemaId] [SchemaId],
	[SysSchema].[UId] [SchemaUId],
	[SysSchema].[Name] [SchemaName],
	[SysPackage].[Name] [PackageName],
	[LocalizableValue].[SysPackageId] [PackageId],
	[LocalizableValue].[SysCultureId] [CultureId],
	[LocalizableValue].[ModifiedOn] [ModifiedOn],
	[LocalizableValue].[Key] [Key],
	[LocalizableValue].[Value] [Value],
	[LocalizableValue].[ResourceType] [ResourceType],
	[LocalizableValue].[ImageData] [ImageData]
FROM
	[dbo].[SysLocalizableValue] [LocalizableValue] WITH(NOLOCK)
	INNER JOIN [dbo].[SysPackage] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([SysPackage].[Id] = [LocalizableValue].[SysPackageId])
	INNER JOIN [dbo].[SysSchema] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([SysSchema].[Id] = [LocalizableValue].[SysSchemaId])
WHERE
	[SysPackage].[SysWorkspaceId] = @P1
	AND [LocalizableValue].[SysSchemaId] IN (@P2, @P3, @P4)) [ResourceSelect]
	INNER JOIN [dbo].[SysPackage] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([SysPackage].[Id] = [ResourceSelect].[PackageId])
ORDER BY
	[PackageLevel] DESC,
	[PackagePosition] DESC,
	[PackageName] ASC

SELECT
	[SysPackage].[Position] [PackagePosition],
	(
SELECT
	MAX([SysPackageHierarchy].[Level])
FROM
	[dbo].[SysPackageHierarchy] WITH(NOLOCK)
WHERE
	[SysPackageHierarchy].[BaseSysPackageId] = [ResourceSelect].[PackageId]) [PackageLevel],
	[ResourceSelect].[SchemaId] [SchemaId],
	[ResourceSelect].[SchemaUId] [SchemaUId],
	[ResourceSelect].[SchemaName] [SchemaName],
	[ResourceSelect].[PackageName] [PackageName],
	[ResourceSelect].[PackageId] [PackageId],
	[ResourceSelect].[CultureId] [CultureId],
	[ResourceSelect].[ModifiedOn] [ModifiedOn],
	[ResourceSelect].[Key] [Key],
	[ResourceSelect].[Value] [Value],
	[ResourceSelect].[ResourceType] [ResourceType],
	[ResourceSelect].[ImageData] [ImageData]
FROM
	(
SELECT
	[LocalizableValue].[SysSchemaId] [SchemaId],
	[SysSchema].[UId] [SchemaUId],
	[SysSchema].[Name] [SchemaName],
	[SysPackage].[Name] [PackageName],
	[LocalizableValue].[SysPackageId] [PackageId],
	[LocalizableValue].[SysCultureId] [CultureId],
	[LocalizableValue].[ModifiedOn] [ModifiedOn],
	[LocalizableValue].[Key] [Key],
	[LocalizableValue].[Value] [Value],
	[LocalizableValue].[ResourceType] [ResourceType],
	[LocalizableValue].[ImageData] [ImageData]
FROM
	[dbo].[SysLocalizableValue] [LocalizableValue] WITH(NOLOCK)
	INNER JOIN [dbo].[SysPackage] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([SysPackage].[Id] = [LocalizableValue].[SysPackageId])
	INNER JOIN [dbo].[SysSchema] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([SysSchema].[Id] = [LocalizableValue].[SysSchemaId])

	[SysPackage].[SysWorkspaceId] = @P1
	AND [LocalizableValue].[SysSchemaId] IN (@P2, @P3, @P4, @P5)) [ResourceSelect]
	INNER JOIN [dbo].[SysPackage] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([SysPackage].[Id] = [ResourceSelect].[PackageId])
ORDER BY
	[PackageLevel] DESC,
	[PackagePosition] DESC,
	[PackageName] ASC

	[SysPackage].[Position] [PackagePosition],
	(
SELECT
	MAX([SysPackageHierarchy].[Level])
FROM
	[dbo].[SysPackageHierarchy] WITH(NOLOCK)
WHERE
	[SysPackageHierarchy].[BaseSysPackageId] = [ResourceSelect].[PackageId]) [PackageLevel],
	[ResourceSelect].[SchemaId] [SchemaId],
	[ResourceSelect].[SchemaUId] [SchemaUId],
	[ResourceSelect].[SchemaName] [SchemaName],
	[ResourceSelect].[PackageName] [PackageName],
	[ResourceSelect].[PackageId] [PackageId],
	[ResourceSelect].[CultureId] [CultureId],
	[ResourceSelect].[ModifiedOn] [ModifiedOn],
	[ResourceSelect].[Key] [Key],
	[ResourceSelect].[Value] [Value],
	[ResourceSelect].[ResourceType] [ResourceType],
	[ResourceSelect].[ImageData] [ImageData]
FROM
	(
SELECT
	[LocalizableValue].[SysSchemaId] [SchemaId],
	[SysSchema].[UId] [SchemaUId],
	[SysSchema].[Name] [SchemaName],
	[SysPackage].[Name] [PackageName],
	[LocalizableValue].[SysPackageId] [PackageId],
	[LocalizableValue].[SysCultureId] [CultureId],
	[LocalizableValue].[ModifiedOn] [ModifiedOn],
	[LocalizableValue].[Key] [Key],
	[LocalizableValue].[Value] [Value],
	[LocalizableValue].[ResourceType] [ResourceType],
	[LocalizableValue].[ImageData] [ImageData]
FROM
	[dbo].[SysLocalizableValue] [LocalizableValue] WITH(NOLOCK)
	INNER JOIN [dbo].[SysPackage] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([SysPackage].[Id] = [LocalizableValue].[SysPackageId])
	INNER JOIN [dbo].[SysSchema] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([SysSchema].[Id] = [LocalizableValue].[SysSchemaId])
WHERE
	[SysPackage].[SysWorkspaceId] = @P1
	AND [LocalizableValue].[SysSchemaId] IN (@P2, @P3)) [ResourceSelect]
	INNER JOIN [dbo].[SysPackage] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([SysPackage].[Id] = [ResourceSelect].[PackageId])
ORDER BY
	[PackageLevel] DESC,
	[PackagePosition] DESC,
	[PackageName] ASC

messageObject.SQL:
SELECT
	[SysPackage].[Position] [PackagePosition],
	(
SELECT
	MAX([SysPackageHierarchy].[Level])
FROM
	[dbo].[SysPackageHierarchy] WITH(NOLOCK)
WHERE
	[SysPackageHierarchy].[BaseSysPackageId] = [ResourceSelect].[PackageId]) [PackageLevel],
	[ResourceSelect].[SchemaId] [SchemaId],
	[ResourceSelect].[SchemaUId] [SchemaUId],
	[ResourceSelect].[SchemaName] [SchemaName],
	[ResourceSelect].[PackageName] [PackageName],
	[ResourceSelect].[PackageId] [PackageId],
	[ResourceSelect].[CultureId] [CultureId],
	[ResourceSelect].[ModifiedOn] [ModifiedOn],
	[ResourceSelect].[Key] [Key],
	[ResourceSelect].[Value] [Value],
	[ResourceSelect].[ResourceType] [ResourceType],
	[ResourceSelect].[ImageData] [ImageData]
FROM
	(
SELECT
	[LocalizableValue].[SysSchemaId] [SchemaId],
	[SysSchema].[UId] [SchemaUId],
	[SysSchema].[Name] [SchemaName],
	[SysPackage].[Name] [PackageName],
	[LocalizableValue].[SysPackageId] [PackageId],
	[LocalizableValue].[SysCultureId] [CultureId],
	[LocalizableValue].[ModifiedOn] [ModifiedOn],
	[LocalizableValue].[Key] [Key],
	[LocalizableValue].[Value] [Value],
	[LocalizableValue].[ResourceType] [ResourceType],
	[LocalizableValue].[ImageData] [ImageData]
FROM
	[dbo].[SysLocalizableValue] [LocalizableValue] WITH(NOLOCK)
	INNER JOIN [dbo].[SysPackage] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([SysPackage].[Id] = [LocalizableValue].[SysPackageId])
	INNER JOIN [dbo].[SysSchema] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([SysSchema].[Id] = [LocalizableValue].[SysSchemaId])
WHERE
	[SysPackage].[SysWorkspaceId] = @P1
	AND [LocalizableValue].[SysSchemaId] IN (@P2, @P3, @P4, @P5)) [ResourceSelect]
	INNER JOIN [dbo].[SysPackage] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([SysPackage].[Id] = [ResourceSelect].[PackageId])
ORDER BY
	[PackageLevel] DESC,
	[PackagePosition] DESC,
	[PackageName] ASC

	[ResourceSelect].[SchemaUId] [SchemaUId],
	[ResourceSelect].[SchemaName] [SchemaName],
	[ResourceSelect].[PackageName] [PackageName],
	[ResourceSelect].[PackageId] [PackageId],
	[ResourceSelect].[CultureId] [CultureId],
	[ResourceSelect].[ModifiedOn] [ModifiedOn],
	[ResourceSelect].[Key] [Key],
	[ResourceSelect].[Value] [Value],

	[ResourceSelect].[ImageData] [ImageData]

	(
SELECT
	[LocalizableValue].[SysSchemaId] [SchemaId],
	[SysSchema].[UId] [SchemaUId],
	[SysSchema].[Name] [SchemaName],
	[SysPackage].[Name] [PackageName],
	[LocalizableValue].[SysPackageId] [PackageId],
	[LocalizableValue].[SysCultureId] [CultureId],
	[LocalizableValue].[ModifiedOn] [ModifiedOn],
	[LocalizableValue].[Key] [Key],
	[LocalizableValue].[Value] [Value],
	[LocalizableValue].[ResourceType] [ResourceType],
	[LocalizableValue].[ImageData] [ImageData]

	[dbo].[SysLocalizableValue] [LocalizableValue] WITH(NOLOCK)
	INNER JOIN [dbo].[SysPackage] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([SysPackage].[Id] = [LocalizableValue].[SysPackageId])

	[PackageLevel] DESC,
	[PackagePosition] DESC,
	[PackageName] ASC

SELECT
	[SysPackage].[Position] [PackagePosition],
	(
SELECT
	MAX([SysPackageHierarchy].[Level])
FROM
	[dbo].[SysPackageHierarchy] WITH(NOLOCK)
WHERE
	[SysPackageHierarchy].[BaseSysPackageId] = [ResourceSelect].[PackageId]) [PackageLevel],
	[ResourceSelect].[SchemaId] [SchemaId],
	[ResourceSelect].[SchemaUId] [SchemaUId],
	[ResourceSelect].[SchemaName] [SchemaName],
	[ResourceSelect].[PackageName] [PackageName],
	[ResourceSelect].[PackageId] [PackageId],
	[ResourceSelect].[CultureId] [CultureId],
	[ResourceSelect].[ModifiedOn] [ModifiedOn],
	[ResourceSelect].[Key] [Key],
	[ResourceSelect].[Value] [Value],
	[ResourceSelect].[ResourceType] [ResourceType],
	[ResourceSelect].[ImageData] [ImageData]
FROM
	(
SELECT
	[LocalizableValue].[SysSchemaId] [SchemaId],
	[SysSchema].[UId] [SchemaUId],
	[SysSchema].[Name] [SchemaName],
	[SysPackage].[Name] [PackageName],
	[LocalizableValue].[SysPackageId] [PackageId],
	[LocalizableValue].[SysCultureId] [CultureId],
	[LocalizableValue].[ModifiedOn] [ModifiedOn],
	[LocalizableValue].[Key] [Key],
	[LocalizableValue].[Value] [Value],
	[LocalizableValue].[ResourceType] [ResourceType],
	[LocalizableValue].[ImageData] [ImageData]
FROM
	[dbo].[SysLocalizableValue] [LocalizableValue] WITH(NOLOCK)
	INNER JOIN [dbo].[SysPackage] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([SysPackage].[Id] = [LocalizableValue].[SysPackageId])
	INNER JOIN [dbo].[SysSchema] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([SysSchema].[Id] = [LocalizableValue].[SysSchemaId])
WHERE
	[SysPackage].[SysWorkspaceId] = @P1
	AND [LocalizableValue].[SysSchemaId] IN (@P2, @P3)) [ResourceSelect]
	INNER JOIN [dbo].[SysPackage] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([SysPackage].[Id] = [ResourceSelect].[PackageId])
ORDER BY
	[PackageLevel] DESC,
	[PackagePosition] DESC,
	[PackageName] ASC

	INNER JOIN [dbo].[SysPackage] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([SysPackage].[Id] = [LocalizableValue].[SysPackageId])
	INNER JOIN [dbo].[SysSchema] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([SysSchema].[Id] = [LocalizableValue].[SysSchemaId])
WHERE
	[SysPackage].[SysWorkspaceId] = @P1
	AND [LocalizableValue].[SysSchemaId] IN (@P2, @P3)) [ResourceSelect]
	INNER JOIN [dbo].[SysPackage] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([SysPackage].[Id] = [ResourceSelect].[PackageId])
ORDER BY
	[PackageLevel] DESC,
	[PackagePosition] DESC,
	[PackageName] ASC

	[SysSettingsValue].[SysAdminUnitId],

	[SysSettingsValue].[IntegerValue],
	[SysSettingsValue].[FloatValue],
	[SysSettingsValue].[BooleanValue],
	[SysSettingsValue].[DateTimeValue],
	[SysSettingsValue].[GuidValue],
	[SysSettingsValue].[BinaryValue]
FROM
	[dbo].[SysSettings] WITH(NOLOCK)
	INNER JOIN [dbo].[SysSettingsValue] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([SysSettings].[Id] = [SysSettingsValue].[SysSettingsId])
	INNER JOIN [dbo].[SysAdminUnit] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([SysAdminUnit].[Id] = [SysSettingsValue].[SysAdminUnitId])

	[SysSettings].[IsCacheable] = @P1
	AND (([SysAdminUnit].[SysAdminUnitTypeValue] <> @P2
	AND [SysAdminUnit].[SysAdminUnitTypeValue] <> @P3)
	OR [SysAdminUnit].[Id] = @P4)
ORDER BY
	[SysSettings].[Code] ASC,
	[SysSettingsValue].[Position] ASC

SELECT
	[Code],
	[OperationGrantee].[CanExecute]
FROM
	[dbo].[SysAdminOperation] WITH(NOLOCK)
	LEFT OUTER JOIN (
SELECT DISTINCT
	[OperationGrantee].[SysAdminOperationId],
	[OperationGrantee].[CanExecute]
FROM
	[dbo].[SysAdminOperationGrantee] [OperationGrantee] WITH(NOLOCK)
	INNER JOIN (
SELECT
	[MinPosition].[SysAdminOperationId],
	MIN([MinPosition].[Position]) [MinPosition]
FROM
	[dbo].[SysAdminOperationGrantee] [MinPosition] WITH(NOLOCK)
	INNER JOIN [dbo].[SysAdminUnitInRole] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([SysAdminUnitInRole].[SysAdminUnitRoleId] = [MinPosition].[SysAdminUnitId])
WHERE
	[SysAdminUnitInRole].[SysAdminUnitId] = @P1
GROUP BY
	[MinPosition].[SysAdminOperationId]) [MinPosition] ON ([MinPosition].[SysAdminOperationId] = [OperationGrantee].[SysAdminOperationId]
	AND [MinPosition].[MinPosition] = [OperationGrantee].[Position])) [OperationGrantee] ON ([Id] = [OperationGrantee].[SysAdminOperationId])

SELECT
	[SysPackage].[Position] [PackagePosition],
	(
SELECT
	MAX([SysPackageHierarchy].[Level])
FROM
	[dbo].[SysPackageHierarchy] WITH(NOLOCK)
WHERE
	[SysPackageHierarchy].[BaseSysPackageId] = [ResourceSelect].[PackageId]) [PackageLevel],
	[ResourceSelect].[SchemaId] [SchemaId],
	[ResourceSelect].[SchemaUId] [SchemaUId],
	[ResourceSelect].[SchemaName] [SchemaName],
	[ResourceSelect].[PackageName] [PackageName],
	[ResourceSelect].[PackageId] [PackageId],
	[ResourceSelect].[CultureId] [CultureId],
	[ResourceSelect].[ModifiedOn] [ModifiedOn],
	[ResourceSelect].[Key] [Key],
	[ResourceSelect].[Value] [Value],
	[ResourceSelect].[ResourceType] [ResourceType],
	[ResourceSelect].[ImageData] [ImageData]
FROM
	(
SELECT
	[LocalizableValue].[SysSchemaId] [SchemaId],
	[SysSchema].[UId] [SchemaUId],
	[SysSchema].[Name] [SchemaName],
	[SysPackage].[Name] [PackageName],
	[LocalizableValue].[SysPackageId] [PackageId],
	[LocalizableValue].[SysCultureId] [CultureId],
	[LocalizableValue].[ModifiedOn] [ModifiedOn],
	[LocalizableValue].[Key] [Key],
	[LocalizableValue].[Value] [Value],
	[LocalizableValue].[ResourceType] [ResourceType],
	[LocalizableValue].[ImageData] [ImageData]
FROM
	[dbo].[SysLocalizableValue] [LocalizableValue] WITH(NOLOCK)
	INNER JOIN [dbo].[SysPackage] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([SysPackage].[Id] = [LocalizableValue].[SysPackageId])
	INNER JOIN [dbo].[SysSchema] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([SysSchema].[Id] = [LocalizableValue].[SysSchemaId])
WHERE
	[SysPackage].[SysWorkspaceId] = @P1
	AND [LocalizableValue].[SysSchemaId] IN (@P2, @P3, @P4)) [ResourceSelect]
	INNER JOIN [dbo].[SysPackage] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([SysPackage].[Id] = [ResourceSelect].[PackageId])
ORDER BY
	[PackageLevel] DESC,
	[PackagePosition] DESC,
	[PackageName] ASC

SELECT
	[LocalizableValue].[SysSchemaId] [SchemaId],
	[SysSchema].[UId] [SchemaUId],
	[SysSchema].[Name] [SchemaName],
	[SysPackage].[Name] [PackageName],
	[LocalizableValue].[SysPackageId] [PackageId],
	[LocalizableValue].[SysCultureId] [CultureId],
	[LocalizableValue].[ModifiedOn] [ModifiedOn],
	[LocalizableValue].[Key] [Key],
	[LocalizableValue].[Value] [Value],
	[LocalizableValue].[ResourceType] [ResourceType],
	[LocalizableValue].[ImageData] [ImageData]
FROM
	[dbo].[SysLocalizableValue] [LocalizableValue] WITH(NOLOCK)

	[PackagePosition] DESC,
	[PackageName] ASC

SELECT
	[SysPackage].[Position] [PackagePosition],
	(
SELECT
	MAX([SysPackageHierarchy].[Level])
FROM
	[dbo].[SysPackageHierarchy] WITH(NOLOCK)
WHERE
	[SysPackageHierarchy].[BaseSysPackageId] = [ResourceSelect].[PackageId]) [PackageLevel],
	[ResourceSelect].[SchemaId] [SchemaId],
	[ResourceSelect].[SchemaUId] [SchemaUId],
	[ResourceSelect].[SchemaName] [SchemaName],
	[ResourceSelect].[PackageName] [PackageName],
	[ResourceSelect].[PackageId] [PackageId],
	[ResourceSelect].[CultureId] [CultureId],
	[ResourceSelect].[ModifiedOn] [ModifiedOn],
	[ResourceSelect].[Key] [Key],
	[ResourceSelect].[Value] [Value],
	[ResourceSelect].[ResourceType] [ResourceType],
	[ResourceSelect].[ImageData] [ImageData]
FROM
	(
SELECT
	[LocalizableValue].[SysSchemaId] [SchemaId],
	[SysSchema].[UId] [SchemaUId],
	[SysSchema].[Name] [SchemaName],
	[SysPackage].[Name] [PackageName],
	[LocalizableValue].[SysPackageId] [PackageId],
	[LocalizableValue].[SysCultureId] [CultureId],
	[LocalizableValue].[ModifiedOn] [ModifiedOn],
	[LocalizableValue].[Key] [Key],
	[LocalizableValue].[Value] [Value],
	[LocalizableValue].[ResourceType] [ResourceType],
	[LocalizableValue].[ImageData] [ImageData]
FROM
	[dbo].[SysLocalizableValue] [LocalizableValue] WITH(NOLOCK)
	INNER JOIN [dbo].[SysPackage] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([SysPackage].[Id] = [LocalizableValue].[SysPackageId])
	INNER JOIN [dbo].[SysSchema] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([SysSchema].[Id] = [LocalizableValue].[SysSchemaId])
WHERE
	[SysPackage].[SysWorkspaceId] = @P1
	AND [LocalizableValue].[SysSchemaId] IN (@P2, @P3)) [ResourceSelect]
	INNER JOIN [dbo].[SysPackage] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([SysPackage].[Id] = [ResourceSelect].[PackageId])
ORDER BY
	[PackageLevel] DESC,
	[PackagePosition] DESC,
	[PackageName] ASC

messageObject.SQL:
SELECT
	[SysPackage].[Position] [PackagePosition],
	(
SELECT
	MAX([SysPackageHierarchy].[Level])
FROM
	[dbo].[SysPackageHierarchy] WITH(NOLOCK)
WHERE
	[SysPackageHierarchy].[BaseSysPackageId] = [ResourceSelect].[PackageId]) [PackageLevel],
	[ResourceSelect].[SchemaId] [SchemaId],
	[ResourceSelect].[SchemaUId] [SchemaUId],
	[ResourceSelect].[SchemaName] [SchemaName],
	[ResourceSelect].[PackageName] [PackageName],
	[ResourceSelect].[PackageId] [PackageId],
	[ResourceSelect].[CultureId] [CultureId],
	[ResourceSelect].[ModifiedOn] [ModifiedOn],
	[ResourceSelect].[Key] [Key],
	[ResourceSelect].[Value] [Value],
	[ResourceSelect].[ResourceType] [ResourceType],
	[ResourceSelect].[ImageData] [ImageData]
FROM
	(
SELECT
	[LocalizableValue].[SysSchemaId] [SchemaId],
	[SysSchema].[UId] [SchemaUId],
	[SysSchema].[Name] [SchemaName],
	[SysPackage].[Name] [PackageName],
	[LocalizableValue].[SysPackageId] [PackageId],
	[LocalizableValue].[SysCultureId] [CultureId],
	[LocalizableValue].[ModifiedOn] [ModifiedOn],
	[LocalizableValue].[Key] [Key],
	[LocalizableValue].[Value] [Value],
	[LocalizableValue].[ResourceType] [ResourceType],
	[LocalizableValue].[ImageData] [ImageData]
FROM
	[dbo].[SysLocalizableValue] [LocalizableValue] WITH(NOLOCK)
	INNER JOIN [dbo].[SysPackage] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([SysPackage].[Id] = [LocalizableValue].[SysPackageId])
	INNER JOIN [dbo].[SysSchema] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([SysSchema].[Id] = [LocalizableValue].[SysSchemaId])
WHERE
	[SysPackage].[SysWorkspaceId] = @P1
	AND [LocalizableValue].[SysSchemaId] IN (@P2, @P3)) [ResourceSelect]
	INNER JOIN [dbo].[SysPackage] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([SysPackage].[Id] = [ResourceSelect].[PackageId])
ORDER BY
	[PackageLevel] DESC,
	[PackagePosition] DESC,
	[PackageName] ASC

	[SysSettingsValue].[BooleanValue],
	[SysSettingsValue].[DateTimeValue],

	[SysSettings].[Code] ASC,
	[SysSettingsValue].[Position] ASC

SELECT
	[Code],
	[OperationGrantee].[CanExecute]
FROM
	[dbo].[SysAdminOperation] WITH(NOLOCK)
	LEFT OUTER JOIN (
SELECT DISTINCT
	[OperationGrantee].[SysAdminOperationId],
	[OperationGrantee].[CanExecute]
FROM
	[dbo].[SysAdminOperationGrantee] [OperationGrantee] WITH(NOLOCK)
	INNER JOIN (
SELECT
	[MinPosition].[SysAdminOperationId],
	MIN([MinPosition].[Position]) [MinPosition]
FROM
	[dbo].[SysAdminOperationGrantee] [MinPosition] WITH(NOLOCK)
	INNER JOIN [dbo].[SysAdminUnitInRole] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([SysAdminUnitInRole].[SysAdminUnitRoleId] = [MinPosition].[SysAdminUnitId])
WHERE
	[SysAdminUnitInRole].[SysAdminUnitId] = @P1
GROUP BY
	[MinPosition].[SysAdminOperationId]) [MinPosition] ON ([MinPosition].[SysAdminOperationId] = [OperationGrantee].[SysAdminOperationId]
	AND [MinPosition].[MinPosition] = [OperationGrantee].[Position])) [OperationGrantee] ON ([Id] = [OperationGrantee].[SysAdminOperationId])

SELECT DISTINCT
	[OperationGrantee].[SysAdminOperationId],
	[OperationGrantee].[CanExecute]
FROM
	[dbo].[SysAdminOperationGrantee] [OperationGrantee] WITH(NOLOCK)
	INNER JOIN (
SELECT
	[MinPosition].[SysAdminOperationId],
	MIN([MinPosition].[Position]) [MinPosition]
FROM
	[dbo].[SysAdminOperationGrantee] [MinPosition] WITH(NOLOCK)
	INNER JOIN [dbo].[SysAdminUnitInRole] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([SysAdminUnitInRole].[SysAdminUnitRoleId] = [MinPosition].[SysAdminUnitId])
WHERE
	[SysAdminUnitInRole].[SysAdminUnitId] = @P1
GROUP BY
	[MinPosition].[SysAdminOperationId]) [MinPosition] ON ([MinPosition].[SysAdminOperationId] = [OperationGrantee].[SysAdminOperationId]
	AND [MinPosition].[MinPosition] = [OperationGrantee].[Position])) [OperationGrantee] ON ([Id] = [OperationGrantee].[SysAdminOperationId])

	[dbo].[SysAdminOperation] WITH(NOLOCK)

SELECT DISTINCT
	[OperationGrantee].[SysAdminOperationId],
	[OperationGrantee].[CanExecute]
FROM
	[dbo].[SysAdminOperationGrantee] [OperationGrantee] WITH(NOLOCK)
	INNER JOIN (
SELECT
	[MinPosition].[SysAdminOperationId],
	MIN([MinPosition].[Position]) [MinPosition]
FROM
	[dbo].[SysAdminOperationGrantee] [MinPosition] WITH(NOLOCK)
	INNER JOIN [dbo].[SysAdminUnitInRole] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([SysAdminUnitInRole].[SysAdminUnitRoleId] = [MinPosition].[SysAdminUnitId])
WHERE
	[SysAdminUnitInRole].[SysAdminUnitId] = @P1
GROUP BY
	[MinPosition].[SysAdminOperationId]) [MinPosition] ON ([MinPosition].[SysAdminOperationId] = [OperationGrantee].[SysAdminOperationId]
	AND [MinPosition].[MinPosition] = [OperationGrantee].[Position])) [OperationGrantee] ON ([Id] = [OperationGrantee].[SysAdminOperationId])

SELECT
	[Code],
	[OperationGrantee].[CanExecute]
FROM
	[dbo].[SysAdminOperation] WITH(NOLOCK)
	LEFT OUTER JOIN (
SELECT DISTINCT
	[OperationGrantee].[SysAdminOperationId],
	[OperationGrantee].[CanExecute]
FROM
	[dbo].[SysAdminOperationGrantee] [OperationGrantee] WITH(NOLOCK)
	INNER JOIN (
SELECT
	[MinPosition].[SysAdminOperationId],
	MIN([MinPosition].[Position]) [MinPosition]
FROM
	[dbo].[SysAdminOperationGrantee] [MinPosition] WITH(NOLOCK)
	INNER JOIN [dbo].[SysAdminUnitInRole] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([SysAdminUnitInRole].[SysAdminUnitRoleId] = [MinPosition].[SysAdminUnitId])
WHERE
	[SysAdminUnitInRole].[SysAdminUnitId] = @P1
GROUP BY
	[MinPosition].[SysAdminOperationId]) [MinPosition] ON ([MinPosition].[SysAdminOperationId] = [OperationGrantee].[SysAdminOperationId]
	AND [MinPosition].[MinPosition] = [OperationGrantee].[Position])) [OperationGrantee] ON ([Id] = [OperationGrantee].[SysAdminOperationId])

SELECT
	[Code],
	[OperationGrantee].[CanExecute]
FROM
	[dbo].[SysAdminOperation] WITH(NOLOCK)
	LEFT OUTER JOIN (
SELECT DISTINCT
	[OperationGrantee].[SysAdminOperationId],
	[OperationGrantee].[CanExecute]
FROM
	[dbo].[SysAdminOperationGrantee] [OperationGrantee] WITH(NOLOCK)
	INNER JOIN (
SELECT
	[MinPosition].[SysAdminOperationId],
	MIN([MinPosition].[Position]) [MinPosition]
FROM
	[dbo].[SysAdminOperationGrantee] [MinPosition] WITH(NOLOCK)
	INNER JOIN [dbo].[SysAdminUnitInRole] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([SysAdminUnitInRole].[SysAdminUnitRoleId] = [MinPosition].[SysAdminUnitId])
WHERE
	[SysAdminUnitInRole].[SysAdminUnitId] = @P1
GROUP BY
	[MinPosition].[SysAdminOperationId]) [MinPosition] ON ([MinPosition].[SysAdminOperationId] = [OperationGrantee].[SysAdminOperationId]
	AND [MinPosition].[MinPosition] = [OperationGrantee].[Position])) [OperationGrantee] ON ([Id] = [OperationGrantee].[SysAdminOperationId])

	[Code],
	[OperationGrantee].[CanExecute]
FROM
	[dbo].[SysAdminOperation] WITH(NOLOCK)
	LEFT OUTER JOIN (
SELECT DISTINCT
	[OperationGrantee].[SysAdminOperationId],
	[OperationGrantee].[CanExecute]
FROM
	[dbo].[SysAdminOperationGrantee] [OperationGrantee] WITH(NOLOCK)
	INNER JOIN (
SELECT
	[MinPosition].[SysAdminOperationId],
	MIN([MinPosition].[Position]) [MinPosition]
FROM
	[dbo].[SysAdminOperationGrantee] [MinPosition] WITH(NOLOCK)
	INNER JOIN [dbo].[SysAdminUnitInRole] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([SysAdminUnitInRole].[SysAdminUnitRoleId] = [MinPosition].[SysAdminUnitId])
WHERE
	[SysAdminUnitInRole].[SysAdminUnitId] = @P1
GROUP BY
	[MinPosition].[SysAdminOperationId]) [MinPosition] ON ([MinPosition].[SysAdminOperationId] = [OperationGrantee].[SysAdminOperationId]
	AND [MinPosition].[MinPosition] = [OperationGrantee].[Position])) [OperationGrantee] ON ([Id] = [OperationGrantee].[SysAdminOperationId])

SELECT
	[Code],
	[OperationGrantee].[CanExecute]
FROM
	[dbo].[SysAdminOperation] WITH(NOLOCK)
	LEFT OUTER JOIN (
SELECT DISTINCT
	[OperationGrantee].[SysAdminOperationId],
	[OperationGrantee].[CanExecute]
FROM
	[dbo].[SysAdminOperationGrantee] [OperationGrantee] WITH(NOLOCK)
	INNER JOIN (
SELECT
	[MinPosition].[SysAdminOperationId],
	MIN([MinPosition].[Position]) [MinPosition]
FROM
	[dbo].[SysAdminOperationGrantee] [MinPosition] WITH(NOLOCK)
	INNER JOIN [dbo].[SysAdminUnitInRole] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([SysAdminUnitInRole].[SysAdminUnitRoleId] = [MinPosition].[SysAdminUnitId])
WHERE
	[SysAdminUnitInRole].[SysAdminUnitId] = @P1
GROUP BY
	[MinPosition].[SysAdminOperationId]) [MinPosition] ON ([MinPosition].[SysAdminOperationId] = [OperationGrantee].[SysAdminOperationId]
	AND [MinPosition].[MinPosition] = [OperationGrantee].[Position])) [OperationGrantee] ON ([Id] = [OperationGrantee].[SysAdminOperationId])

SELECT
	[SubjectSchemaUId],
	[CanRead],
	[CanAppend],
	[CanEdit],
	[CanDelete]
FROM
	[dbo].[SysEntitySchemaOperationRight] WITH(NOLOCK)
WHERE
	EXISTS (
SELECT
	1
FROM
	[dbo].[SysAdminUnitInRole] WITH(NOLOCK)
WHERE
	[SysAdminUnitInRole].[SysAdminUnitId] = @P1
	AND [SysAdminUnitInRole].[SysAdminUnitRoleId] = [SysEntitySchemaOperationRight].[SysAdminUnitId])
	AND [SysEntitySchemaOperationRight].[Position] = (
SELECT
	MIN([Position])
FROM
	[dbo].[SysEntitySchemaOperationRight] [MinRightPosition] WITH(NOLOCK)
WHERE
	EXISTS (
SELECT
	1
FROM
	[dbo].[SysAdminUnitInRole] WITH(NOLOCK)
WHERE
	[SysAdminUnitInRole].[SysAdminUnitId] = @P2
	AND [SysAdminUnitInRole].[SysAdminUnitRoleId] = [MinRightPosition].[SysAdminUnitId])
	AND [MinRightPosition].[SubjectSchemaUId] = [SysEntitySchemaOperationRight].[SubjectSchemaUId])
